“In KwaMhlanga, the Community Service centre will be operating from the pack homes inside the station premises. Members of the community can call 082-5656-453 for all emergencies and complaints. In White River, the Community Service Centre will now be operating from the White River boardroom behind the CSC. Call 082-303-9618 for all emergencies. In KaMhlushwa the CSC will be operating from KaMhlushwa Community Hall next to Nkomazi Municipal offices. ALSO READ: Kruger Lowveld Tourism concerned about non-compliance regarding Covid-19 regulations The station could be reached at 082-389-8101,” explains Col Donald Mdhluli, the provincial police spokesperson. According to Mdhluli, all three police station will be opened once disinfected.